Standard Unlu, Turkven to Invest in Turkish Ice Cream Producer

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 
2011-05-02T08:19:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-02/standard-unlu-turkven-to-invest-in-turkish-ice-cream-producer.html
Turkish private-equity companies
Standard Unlu Private Equity and  Turkven  said they will invest
together in Ulker Golf, a Turkish ice cream maker.  They set up a venture called Ice Cream Investment BV, which
will become a minority shareholder in Natura Gida, owner of
Ulker Golf, the Istanbul-based investment companies said in an
e-mailed statement today. They said they will announce details
of the partnership at a news conference May 4.  Yildiz Holding AS, a Turkish holding company with
investments in  food production , owns Natura Gida.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net . 